node.text:
Watch to see how we capture Henry + Baloo’s special moments and learn some tips + tricks you can use to photograph your amazing pets! 

#ad Thanks to our friends @samsungmobile we filmed everything with our #GalaxyS21 Ultra for the new Master It creator classes, and wow ... it is incredible. Seriously can’t wait to share some more photos/videos with you and show you how to #MasterIt #withGalaxy

node.text:
BIG news!! We’ve teamed up with our friends @omaze to give you the chance to WIN a 4x4 Sprinter Van with an $80,000 eco-friendly conversion - all while supporting a great cause 🙌🏽 #sponsored This van has everything you need for any adventure (even roof solar panels to keep you powered up) and every donation supports the @honnoldfoundation.

You can enter for your chance to win this amazing 4x4 Sprinter Van at the link in my bio or go to 
omaze.com/henrybaloo ❤️ Good luck guys!! #omaze

node.text:
Humans and furry friends you have to stream Turner & Hooch, an Original Series now streaming on @DisneyPlus! #ad This series is about Hooch, an amazing canine U.S. Marshall, who fights crime alongside his human BFF, Turner. They are besties that do everything together, even though their friendship was unlikely from the start.. just like us! 

Turner & Hooch chasing bad guys is as thrilling as seeing your friends at the dog park and Josh Peck, aka Turner, is so funny! Guaranteed to have a good belly laugh. If I weren’t climbing mountains and swimming in rivers, I’d want to be chasing bad guys just like Hooch. 5/5 Paws! -♥️ Henry 
#TurnerAndHoochSeries #DisneyPlus

node.text:
Happy Birthday Baloo!!❤️🎉

We celebrated B’s 4th birthday yesterday with a backpacking trip to his happy place. Every time we come here, he chases bugs for hours in this alpine meadow until it gets so dark that we have to make him come in the tent 🐛 This year we even attached a mini light to his harness so the bugs would be drawn right to him! 

Don’t tell Baloo, but tonight he’s getting a Tuna fish cake and lots of presents to open 🤫 We love you so much little B, hope you’re 4th birthday was the best one yet!

node.text: We’re back from Montana and can’t wait to share this trip with you guys! MT was so beautiful and we even saw a herd of wild horses on our drive home (swipe to see) 😱

node.text:
Last night we had such a fun adventure filled with mountain views, fields of wildflowers, a beautiful sunset, and #PrimeTreats for the furkids! 

H+B are super excited to be partnering with @purinaprimetreats this summer. Henry said his favorite flavor is the all-natural Prime Jerky Tenders with Turkey and to make sure to always bring them on the trail! He can have as many as he wants too because they have no corn, no wheat, no soy, and no artificial colors or preservatives. 🧡 
#sponsored

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Henry + Baloo in Road Trip. May be an image of 1 person and animal.

node.text:
We’re all packed + headed to Montana to visit my grandparents! Henry & Baloo haven’t met them yet and we’re so excited this is finally happening 💚 

My grandparents live on the East Coast which has made visiting them with H+B a bit difficult. But MT is much much closer, so we jumped on the opportunity for everyone to meet and spend some quality time together!! See you soon Boppa and Gram, we can’t WAIT 😊
